this adds the summoning int needed for the "need leveling" in client.java

now go to wearing.java

search for 

[code]	public int GetCLCrafting(int ItemID) {
		if (ItemID == -1) {
			return 1;
[/code]

at the end of }

so at end of this
[code]	public int GetCLCrafting(int ItemID) {
		if (ItemID == -1) {
			return 1;
		}
		String ItemName = GetItemName(ItemID);
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Crafting cape")) {
			return 99;
		}
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Crafting hood")) {
			return 99;
		}
		return 1;
	}
[/code]

add your skill like this:

[code]		public int GetCLSummoning(int ItemID) {
		if (ItemID == -1) {
			return 1;
		}
		String ItemName = GetItemName(ItemID);
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Summoning cape")) {
			return 99;
		}
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Summoning hood")) {
			return 99;
		}
		return 1;
	}
[/code]

what this does is tell the server what level is needed for that certain skill an EX my summoning cape 

[code]		if (ItemName.startsWith("Summoning cape")) 
[/code]
